rustysword.name: Rusty Sword
rustysword.description: Makes cards containing Samurai or Insomniac more likely to be pulled.

cafemixtape.name: Cafe Mixtape
cafemixtape.description: Makes cards containing Cole Brew or coffeeshop workers more likely to be pulled.

oversizedstethoscope.name: Oversized Stethoscope
oversizedstethoscope.description: Makes cards containing medical staff more likely to be pulled.

valentinesdaycard.name: Valentine's Day Card
valentinesdaycard.description: Makes cards containing Logan or Hailey more likely to be pulled.

hardcandy.name: Hard Candy
hardcandy.description: Makes cards containing Mr. Stevenson or Mrs. Stevenson more likely to be pulled.

deluxebirdseed.name: Deluxe Birdseed
deluxebirdseed.description: Makes cards containing a bird more likely to be pulled.

fixedmouse.name: Fixed Mouse
fixedmouse.description: Sometimes lets you **Double Click**, and pull two cards at once.

stoppedwatch.name: Stopped Watch
stoppedwatch.description: Brings the c!pull timer down to 10 hours.

faithfulnecklace.name: Faithful Necklace
faithfulnecklace.description: Brings the c!pray timer down to 20 hours.

stainedgloves.name: Stained Gloves
stainedgloves.description:
Brings the c!box timer down to 8 hours.
wait...
were you reaching in there with your bare hands ***this whole time!??!?!?***

paddedstickersheet.name: Padded Sticker Sheet
paddedstickersheet.description: Makes cards containing a custom character (being used as a traditional row) more likely to be pulled.

duncecap.name: Dunce Cap
duncecap.description: Makes meme cards or humorous cards more likely to be pulled.

deviltail.name: Devil Tail
deviltail.description: Makes dark or horror-themed cards more likely to be pulled.

scribblednotepad.name: Scribbled-in Notepad
scribblednotepad.description: Makes editor cards more likely to be pulled.

okamiiscollar.name: okamii's Collar
okamiiscollar.description: Makes Rare cards more likely to be pulled.

lostnametag.name: Lost Name Tag
lostnametag.description: Makes cards containing Farmer or Politician more likely to be pulled.

charcoalpencil.name: Charcoal Pencil
charcoalpencil.description: Makes cards containing Miner or Lucia Moon more likely to be pulled.

fieldjournal.name: Field Journal
fieldjournal.description: Makes cards containing RDRPG Bosses or Levels more likely to be pulled.

driftingmetronome.name: Drifting Metronome
driftingmetronome.description: Makes cards containing Editor characters more likely to be pulled.

filmreel.name: Film Reel
filmreel.description: Makes animated cards more likely to be pulled.

swirlymarbles.name: Swirly Marbles
swirlymarbles.description: Makes ADOFAI cards more likely to be pulled.

sparecryopod.name: Spare Cryopod
sparecryopod.description: Allows storing up to three pulls, which can be used in succession. Stored pulls are removed when the item is taken off.

aceofhearts.name: Ace of Hearts
aceofhearts.description: Every 21 pulls, automatically gain 10 tokens. The pull counter is reset when a consumable is used or the item is taken off.

oldfriend.name: Old Friend
oldfriend.description: A doll made in the likeness of an old friend. It does nothing, but has sentimental value.

mustache.name: Fake Mustache
mustache.description: Decreases the percentage of success of robbing, but gets a shorter time of getting blacklisted.

doubleedge.name: Double Edged Sword
doubleedge.description: Increases the percentage of success of robbing, but gets a longer time of getting blacklisted.
